<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Demo 1 - Foundation Infrastructure Control Panel</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0f19;
            --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --text-primary: #f3f4f6;
            --text-secondary: #9ca3af;
            --accent-blue: #3b82f6;
            --accent-purple: #8b5cf6;
            --accent-green: #10b981;
            --glow-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(at 10% 20%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 90% 80%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0px, transparent 50%);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        header {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            color: #60a5fa;
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 30%, #a5b4fc 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.2s both;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: left;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: transparent;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card-nginx::before { background: var(--accent-green); }
        .card-grafana::before { background: #ff9e1b; }
        .card-n8n::before { background: #ff6d5a; }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 0 15px var(--glow-color);
        }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .status {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 16px;
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
            color: #34d399;
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background-color: var(--accent-green);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent-green);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            padding-top: 24px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease 0.4s both;
        }

        .system-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .info-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="badge">AWS Foundation Environment</div>
            <h1 id="main-title">Infrastructure Hub</h1>
            <p class="description">Access operational monitoring, workflow automation, and infrastructure proxy details running on EC2 via secure routing.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="grid">
            <!-- Nginx -->
            <a href="#" class="card card-nginx" id="btn-nginx-proxy">
                <span class="card-icon">🎯</span>
                <h2>NGINX Reverse Proxy</h2>
                <p>Configured as the primary gateway, directing HTTP/HTTPS traffic to internal tool ports with route mapping.</p>
                <div class="status"><span class="status-dot"></span>Active</div>
            </a>

            <!-- Grafana -->
            <a href="/grafana/" class="card card-grafana" id="btn-grafana-link">
                <span class="card-icon">📊</span>
                <h2>Grafana Dashboards</h2>
                <p>Visualize system metrics, CPU/memory performance, container health, and database statistics.</p>
                <div class="status"><span class="status-dot"></span>Active</div>
            </a>

            <!-- Prometheus -->
            <a href="/prometheus/" class="card card-nginx" id="btn-prometheus-link">
                <span class="card-icon">🕰️</span>
                <h2>Prometheus Monitoring</h2>
                <p>Time-series metrics engine collecting data points from system exporters at configured scrape intervals.</p>
                <div class="status"><span class="status-dot"></span>Active</div>
            </a>

            <!-- N8n -->
            <a href="/n8n/" class="card card-n8n" id="btn-n8n-link">
                <span class="card-icon">⚡</span>
                <h2>N8n Workflow Automation</h2>
                <p>Deploy node-based integration playbooks and run event-driven automations connected to AWS RDS.</p>
                <div class="status"><span class="status-dot"></span>Active</div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Antigravity DevOps Systems. Provisioned automatically via Terraform & Ansible.</p>
            <div class="system-info">
                <span class="info-item">EC2: {{ ansible_facts['processor'] | default('t3.medium') }}</span>
                <span class="info-item">OS: Ubuntu {{ ansible_facts['distribution_version'] | default('22.04') }}</span>
                <span class="info-item">Bastion Host: Port 22 Enabled</span>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
